title: Gorgeous 4 Bedroom 2.5 Baths Executive Home Lease Purchase!!
posting_body: ["This is the opportunity that you've been looking for!", ' Almost new, spacious open floor plan home with all the bells and whistles!', " This home features a chef's kitchen with granite counter tops, loads of cabinets, center island and wood flooring.", '  Oversized master suite with garden bath and huge walk-in closet.', ' All secondary bedrooms are a good size too!', ' Lovely rear yard with covered patio to enjoy the barbeques!!', 'Just minutes to the Mall of Georgia, restaurants and shopping!', 'Requires:', 'Minimum Trans Union Score 620', 'Qualifying / Verifiable Income', 'Good Housing History', 'Not Currently in Bankruptcy or Foreclosure', '***NO DOWN PAYMENT REQUIRED***', 'Contact me for more info and appointment to see the home!', 'Arthur Boyd', 'Licensed Agent', 'Keller Williams Realty', 'Mobile', 'show contact info', 'Office  678-57-2700', 'This home is being offered for sale for $483,000.00', 'Listing info provided by courtesy of Open Door', 'Lease Purchase Program offered through Home Partners of America']
